main.ts:
namespace SpriteKind {
    export const Hitbox = SpriteKind.create()
}
controller.B.onEvent(ControllerButtonEvent.Pressed, function () {
    projectile = sprites.createProjectileFromSprite(img`
        . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 
        . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 
        . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 
        . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 
        . . . . . . . . b b b b . . . . 
        . . . . . . . . b b b b b b . . 
        . d d d d . . . . b b b b b b . 
        e e e e e e e e e b b b b b b b 
        . d d d d . . . . b b b b b b . 
        . . . . . . . . b b b b b b . . 
        . . . . . . . . b b b b . . . . 
        . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 
        . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 
        . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 
        . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 
        . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 
        `, mySprite, mySprite.vx * 3, mySprite.vy * 3)
    projectile.setPosition(mySprite.x, mySprite.y)
    projectile.startEffect(effects.spray, 5000)
})
controller.A.onEvent(ControllerButtonEvent.Pressed, function () {
    MapID += 1
})
info.onLifeZero(function () {
    game.gameOver(false)
})
let MapID = 0
let projectile: Sprite = null
let mySprite: Sprite = null
tiles.setCurrentTilemap(tilemap`level`)
mySprite = sprites.create(img`
    ....................
    ....................
    ....................
    ....................
    ....................
    ....................
    .....7977777777.....
    .....7777777777.....
    ......66666666......
    ......77777777......
    .....7797777777.....
    .....7977777777.....
    .....7977777777.....
    .....7777777777.....
    .....7777777777.....
    .....77f7777f76.....
    .....7777ff7776.....
    ......76666666......
    .......f....f.......
    .......f....f.......
    `, SpriteKind.Player)
mySprite.setPosition(125, 105)
let HealthofPLR = statusbars.create(40, 4, StatusBarKind.Health)
info.setLife(3)
HealthofPLR.max = 100
HealthofPLR.setStatusBarFlag(StatusBarFlag.SmoothTransition, true)
scene.cameraFollowSprite(mySprite)
HealthofPLR.attachToSprite(mySprite)
HealthofPLR.setLabel("HP")
HealthofPLR.setColor(7, 15, 2)
HealthofPLR.value = 100
controller.moveSprite(mySprite, 50, 50)
let tptonextllvl = sprites.create(assets.image`Debug`, SpriteKind.Hitbox)
pause(500)
grid.snap(tptonextllvl, false)
grid.place(tptonextllvl, tiles.getTileLocation(0, 12))
scaling.scaleToPixels(tptonextllvl, 90, ScaleDirection.Vertically, ScaleAnchor.Top)
tiles.setCurrentTilemap(tilemap`level`)
forever(function () {
    if (MapID == 0) {
        tiles.setCurrentTilemap(tilemap`level`)
    } else if (MapID == 1) {
        tiles.setCurrentTilemap(tilemap`Grasslands2`)
    } else {
        tiles.setCurrentTilemap(tilemap`level1Dungeon`)
    }
})
forever(function () {
	
})
